<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF108-044-124  </DOCNO><DOCID>08 044 124.andO;</DOCID><JOURNAL>Computer Reseller News  Jan 8 1990 n349 p49(1).andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>SoftSolutions to rescue: 'PerfectSolution' archives, locatesdocuments on LANs. (local area networks) (product announcement)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Mehta, Suketu.andM;</AUTHOR><TEXT><ABSTRACT>SoftSolutions introduces PerfectSolution, the most advanceddocument management software on the market, but also the mostexpensive.andP;  At $2,495 per server, PerfectSolution organizes,archives and locates documents on a local area network (LAN).andP;  Thesoftware builds a document profile whenever a document on anetwork is created.andP;  Its unique feature is its ability to dofull-text searches with the use of an algorithm dubbedSpeedSearch.andP;  Other features include: a report writer, a billingfunction and an echoing feature.andP;  PerfectSolution requires160Kbyte of RAM upon installation but when loading a document intoan application, the required RAM for background operation isreduced to 18Kbytes.andM;</ABSTRACT></TEXT><DESCRIPT>Company:   SoftSolutions Inc. (product introduction).andO;Product:   PerfectSolution (Computer network software) (productintroduction).andO;Topic:     Product IntroductionLocal Area NetworksDocument Management SystemsSoftware Packages.andM;</DESCRIPT></DOC>